OL,3,CDisused hotel fire treated as arson
OL,5,FA fire at a disused hotel which forced
OL,6,Fthe evacuation of neighbouring
OL,7,Fproperties is being treated as arson.
OL,9,FThe incident started at the former
OL,10,FBalmoral Hotel, on Fort Terrace, at
OL,11,Fabout 9.30pm on Tuesday.
OL,13,FPeople were told to leave adjacent
OL,14,Fbuildings while fire crews
OL,15,Fextinguished the flames.
OL,17,FA Humberside Police spokesperson said
OL,18,Fit was being investigated as arson.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
