OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1777558268
OL,3,CDisused hotel fire treated as arson
OL,5,FThey added: "Extensive enquires remain
OL,6,Fongoing to establish the full
OL,7,Fcircumstances surrounding the incident.
OL,9,F"At this time, we have not received
OL,10,Fany reports of injuries sustained as a
OL,11,Fresult of the fire, and officers
OL,12,Fremain in the area conducting lines of
OL,13,Fenquiry to identify those involved.
OL,15,F"Road closures were in place to allow
OL,16,Femergency services to work safely, and
OL,17,Fwe can confirm these have now been
OL,18,Flifted."
OL,20,FThe former 34-bedroom hotel has been
OL,21,Fclosed since 2019.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
