OL,3,CDisused hotel fire treated as arson
OL,5,FThe fire was the second at the hotel
OL,6,Fin the space of five months after an
OL,7,Fincident in December led to the
OL,8,Fdiscovery of a cannabis factory with
OL,9,Fnearly 200 plants.
OL,11,FEast Riding County Council said the
OL,12,Fnearby leisure centre was "open as
OL,13,Fnormal" despite road closures.
